In the MATTER OF the License of Cheryl ACKERMAN, M.D., License No. 25MA06096100 To Practice Medicine and Surgery in the State of New Jersey M-1426 September Term 2017
080161 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 6, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion of Cheryl Ackerman for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the motion to vacate the order of dismissal and reinstate the notice of petition for certification is denied.
